# RHOAI Version Compatibility

## Supported Versions

| Version | Channel Options | Use Case |
|---------|-----------------|----------|
| RHOAI 3.3 | `fast-3.x`, `stable-3.3` | Latest — MaaS, llm-d, Llama Stack 0.4.2 |
| RHOAI 3.2 | `fast-3.x`, `stable-3.2` | Production with GenAI, MaaS |
| RHOAI 2.25 | `stable` | Workshops, demos |
| RHOAI 2.22, 2.19 | `stable-X.Y` | Legacy |

Channels vary by cluster. Check with:
```bash
oc get packagemanifest rhods-operator -n openshift-marketplace -o jsonpath='{.status.channels[*].name}'
```

## RHOAI 3.3 Changes (vs 3.2)

- **Kubeflow Trainer v2** — GA, requires JobSet operator, use `trainer` not `trainingoperator`
- **MLServer ServingRuntime** — Tech Preview for scikit-learn, XGBoost
- **Llama Stack 0.4.2** — OpenAI-compatible RAG annotations
- **MaaS Zero-Touch** — via `modelsAsService` in DSC
- **NVIDIA NIM** — `kserve.nim.managementState: Managed`
- **MLflow Operator** — experiment tracking
- **Dashboard URL** — `data-science-gateway.apps.<cluster>` (was `rhods-dashboard`)
- **CodeFlare removed** — use KubeRay directly
- **Resource naming** — `data-science-` prefix
- **Feature Store** — stricter label/restAPI requirements for dashboard visibility

## Component Dependency Matrix

| Component | Required Dependencies |
|-----------|----------------------|
| Workbenches | None |
| AI Pipelines | S3-compatible storage |
| Kueue/Distributed Workloads | Kueue Operator, cert-manager |
| Model Serving (KServe) | cert-manager |
| Distributed Inference (llm-d) | cert-manager, RHCL, LWS |
| Llama Stack/RAG | Llama Stack Op, Service Mesh 3, cert-manager, NFD, GPU Op |
| Model Registry | MySQL 5.x/8.x, S3 storage |
| GPU Acceleration | NVIDIA GPU Operator, NFD |
| Trainer (Kubeflow v2) | JobSet operator |

## Operator Channels & Packages

| Operator | Package Name | Channel | Namespace |
|----------|-------------|---------|-----------|
| NFD | `nfd` | `stable` | `openshift-nfd` |
| GPU | `gpu-operator-certified` | `v25.10` | `nvidia-gpu-operator` |
| Kueue | `kueue-operator` | `stable-v1.3` | `openshift-operators` |
| LWS | `leader-worker-set` | `stable-v1.0` | `openshift-lws-operator` |
| cert-manager | `openshift-cert-manager-operator` | `stable-v1` | `cert-manager-operator` |
| RHCL/Kuadrant | `connectivity-link-operator` | `stable-1.3` | `redhat-connectivity-link-operator` |

## MaaS Version Differences

- **RHOAI 3.3+**: Integrated MaaS (`modelsAsService` in DataScienceCluster)
  - Endpoint: `inference-gateway.apps.<cluster>`
  - Gateway in `openshift-ingress`
- **RHOAI 3.2-**: Legacy kustomize-based (`maas-api` namespace)
  - Endpoint: `maas.<cluster>/maas-api/v1/...`
  - Setup script auto-detects version

## Dashboard URL by Version

- **RHOAI 3.3+**: `data-science-gateway.apps.<cluster>`
- **RHOAI 3.2-**: `rhods-dashboard-redhat-ods-applications.apps.<cluster>`
